trans-unit.source: By default, any class that inherits from <xref:System.Windows.UIElement3D> uses UIElement3DAutomationPeer to communicate with [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_uiautomation](~/add/includes/tla2sharptla-uiautomation-md.md)].

trans-unit.source: If you create a class that inherits from <xref:System.Windows.UIElement3D>, you may want to provide an automation peer to support the functionality of your class.
trans-unit.target: Om du skapar en klass som ärver från <xref:System.Windows.UIElement3D>, kan du ange en automation peer för att stödja funktionerna i din klass.</xref:System.Windows.UIElement3D>

trans-unit.source: Override the <xref:System.Windows.Automation.Peers.UIElement3DAutomationPeer.GetClassNameCore%2A> method to return a string that represents the type of the element associated with the UIElement3DAutomationPeer.
trans-unit.target: Åsidosätta den <xref:System.Windows.Automation.Peers.UIElement3DAutomationPeer.GetClassNameCore%2A>metod för att returnera en sträng som representerar typ av element som är associerade med UIElement3DAutomationPeer.</xref:System.Windows.Automation.Peers.UIElement3DAutomationPeer.GetClassNameCore%2A>

trans-unit.source: For example, if you create a class called `My3DElement` and an automation peer called `My3DElementAutomationPeer`, override the <xref:System.Windows.Automation.Peers.UIElement3DAutomationPeer.GetClassNameCore%2A> method to return the string "My3DElement".
trans-unit.target: Till exempel om du skapar en klass med namnet `My3DElement` och en automation peer kallas `My3DElementAutomationPeer`, åsidosätta den <xref:System.Windows.Automation.Peers.UIElement3DAutomationPeer.GetClassNameCore%2A>metod för att returnera strängen "My3DElement".</xref:System.Windows.Automation.Peers.UIElement3DAutomationPeer.GetClassNameCore%2A>

trans-unit.source: If your class matches one of the known control types, override the <xref:System.Windows.Automation.Peers.UIElement3DAutomationPeer.GetAutomationControlTypeCore%2A> method to return that <xref:System.Windows.Automation.ControlType>.
trans-unit.target: Om klassen matchar något av följande kända kontroll, Åsidosätt <xref:System.Windows.Automation.Peers.UIElement3DAutomationPeer.GetAutomationControlTypeCore%2A>metoden för att returnera den <xref:System.Windows.Automation.ControlType>.</xref:System.Windows.Automation.ControlType> </xref:System.Windows.Automation.Peers.UIElement3DAutomationPeer.GetAutomationControlTypeCore%2A>

trans-unit.source: Note that although the existing <xref:System.Windows.Automation.ControlType> values are generally associated with 2D controls, the <xref:System.Windows.Automation.ControlType> indicates a control's functionality, not its appearance.
trans-unit.target: Observera att även om den befintliga <xref:System.Windows.Automation.ControlType>värden är vanligtvis kopplad till 2D kontroller i <xref:System.Windows.Automation.ControlType>anger en kontroll funktioner, inte dess utseende.</xref:System.Windows.Automation.ControlType> </xref:System.Windows.Automation.ControlType>
